<div id="community-vibe">
    <h2 class="sect-title">Community Vibe in Maple Ridge</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">Maple Ridge is home to Maple Ridge Public Golf Course overlooking the Bow River Valley,making it
                an ideal and scenic place for people who love an occasional 9-hole game. </p>
            <p class="par-xl">At the end of Southland Drive is the Bow River Valley and Southland Dog Park, making Maple Ridge an excellent location for dog owners and avid walkers/runners. </p>
            <p class="par-lg">The community is also located a short drive from Fish Creek Park. South Centre Mall is
                located in the
                adjacent Willow Park community, along with the Trico Leisure Centre, Fish Creek Public Library and
                Anderson LRT Station, granting easy access to downtown via the C-train and various southeast and
                southwest communities via the large quantity of bus routes.</p>
        </div>
